data.description: Are you looking to purchase a move-in ready home or an investment property in a prime Tacoma location? This home is for YOU! Currently an income-producing STR.This charming 1925 2 bed/1 bath home has been completely renovated w/all-new landscaping, flooring,solar panels & a new kitchen. Newer systems include plumbing,side sewer, electrical & newer roof. Inside charm galore w/original architectural finishes blended w/modern updates. Bonus space in attic. Meticulously designed outdoor space for the ultimate outdoor experience. Amenities include poured concrete walkways,7 ft tall fence w/pergola,Hot tub w/covered deck & seating area. Large corner lot,fenced backyard & 1-car garage w/plenty of parking. Seller is willing to leave the furniture!
